    "content": "The verse and chorus are the same. \r\nThe cadences going from the verse into the chorus and \r\ngoing back from the chorus into the verse are the main \r\nvariations on the chord progression.\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------|\r\nD|-------------|\r\nA|-4~----------|\r\nE|----4~-2~-2~-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------|\r\nD|---------|\r\nA|-6~~-----|\r\nE|-----4~~-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Chorus]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------|\r\nD|-------------|\r\nA|-4~----------|\r\nE|----4~-2~-2~-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------|------|\r\nD|-----------|------|\r\nA|-6~~-------|-4----|\r\nE|-----2~-4--|------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse 2]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------|\r\nD|-------|\r\nA|-------|\r\nE|-7h9\\--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------|--------|----|\r\nD|-------|-4-5-6~-|-6\\-|\r\nA|-4h6~~-|--------|----|\r\nE|-------|--------|----|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Chorus]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------|\r\nD|-------------|\r\nA|-4~----------|\r\nE|----4~-2~-2~-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------|------|\r\nD|-----------|------|\r\nA|-6~~-------|-4----|\r\nE|-----2~-4--|------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n[Verse 3] [RAP VERSE]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------|----------------|\r\nD|------------------|----------------|\r\nA|-4-4-4---4/6-6-6--|----------------|\r\nE|----------------4-|-2-2-2-22-2-2-2-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------|----------------|\r\nD|------------------|----4-4---------|\r\nA|-4-4-4---4/6-6-6--|----------------|\r\nE|----------------4-|-22-----22-2-2--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------|----------------|\r\nD|------------------|----------------|\r\nA|-4-4-4---4/6-6-6--|----------------|\r\nE|----------------4-|-2-2-2-22-2-2-2-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------|----------------|\r\nD|------------------|-----4-4-4------|\r\nA|-4-4-4---4/6-6-6--|----------------|\r\nE|----------------4-|-2-2--------2~--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\nVerse 3 is basically the same as the rest of the song but \r\nwith a slight variation, ride the C#, slide up to D#, \r\nthen down to the F# with some octave jumps. \r\nListen to the recording to get an idea.\r\n\r\n\r\n[Chorus]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------|\r\nD|-------------|\r\nA|-4~----------|\r\nE|----4~-2~-2~-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-----------|------|\r\nD|-----------|------|\r\nA|-6~~-------|-4----|\r\nE|-----2~-4--|------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n************************************\r\n\r\n| ~  Vibrato\r\n| .  Staccato\r\n| h  Hammer-on\r\n| \\  Slide down\r\n| /  Slide up\r\n\r\n************************************",
